  "stem": "<p>The expression <math><mi>x</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> is equivalent to <math><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></math>, where <math><mi>a</mi></math> is a constant. What is the value of <math><mi>a</mi></math> ?</p>",
